com.i2group.apollo.service.common

Class DeletionStatusException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.i2group.apollo.service.common.DeletionStatusException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @WebFault
public final class DeletionStatusException
extends Exception
    The exception raised when a service method tries to act upon an Item that is marked as deleted, or tries to undelete an Item that is not marked as deleted.
    Since:
    2.0
